question: <image 1> Select one box to name the interval.
description:
The image shows a musical staff with a treble clef at the beginning. There are two notes on the staff: one note is placed on the second line from the bottom (D line), and the other note is placed on the top line (E line). Below the staff, there are four options listed with checkboxes next to them:

1. compound minor 3rd
2. compound major 3rd
3. compound minor 6th
4. compound major 6th

The task is to select one box to name the interval between the two notes on the staff.
